Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:57.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}毁灭终结的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:07.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无情的宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:20.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你独自听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:33.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我做了一个遥远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该选择什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该决定什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该选择什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}对着神质问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我并非独自一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:58.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身边 对我伸出这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}没什么好害怕的
